law.catch_line: // EFFECTIVE UNTIL MAY 31, 2015 PER CHAPTER 118 OF 2012 //...
law.text:
// EFFECTIVE UNTIL MAY 31, 2015 PER CHAPTER 118 OF 2012 //
In this subtitle the following words have the meanings indicated.
"Baby boomer" means an individual born during the years 1946 through 1964.
"Council" means the Baby Boomer Initiative Council.
